%[text] Part 4)
%[text] 1\) From the simulation, we get $L=0.593987$, $L\_q=0.131955$, $W=0.353286$, and $W\_q=0.038248$. We also get the simulated value $\\pi\_s=0.712468$.
%[text] 3\) 

